Blinding (Romanian: Orbitor) is a novel in three volumes by the Romanian writer Mircea Crtrescu. It consists of the installments Aripa stng ("The left wing") from 1996, Corpul ("The body") from 2002, and Aripa dreapt ("The right wing") from 2007. An English translation is set to be published in 2012.[1]
